            </td>
            <td class="Table Table-Body" style="text-align: left;">
                <p class="Table-Styles_Table-Body--for-Table-Cell-Style-">A master of martial arts, harnessing the power of the body in pursuit of physical and spiritual perfection</p>
            </td>
            <td class="Table Table-Body" style="text-align: center;">
                <p class="Table-Styles_Table-Body--for-Table-Cell-Style-">d8</p>
